1.text: There was a shepherd boy. He looked after a flock of sheep. He took the sheep to the forest every morning. He brought them back in the evening. One day he played a trick with the villagers. He shouted, ''Help, help, there is a wolf''. All the villagers came to save the boy. They asked the boy, ''Where is the wolf?" The boy replied, ''There is no wolf. It's just a trick.''
